      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with its signature individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing system. This example remains in concours-level condition, boasting a rigid chassis with documented subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution across the rear axle, while the suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications. Mechanical integrity is paramount, with recent rod bearing service and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. A rare find for the purist seeking telepathic steering response and a linear power band.",
